---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../../components/PageHeader.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy of Impresa Confidi SCpA — Personal data processing notice according to GDPR (EU Regulation 2016/679)."
  lang="en"
  currentPath="/en/privacy"
>
  <PageHeader title="Privacy Policy" subtitle="Personal data processing notice" />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="prose max-w-none text-text-light space-y-6">

        <p><strong>Last updated: 2026</strong></p>

        <h2 class="text-primary text-2xl mt-10">1. Data Controller</h2>
        <p>The Data Controller is <strong>Impresa Confidi SCpA</strong>, with registered office at Via Cappuccini 64, 80059 Torre del Greco (NA), Italy, Tax Code – VAT: 03375901216, email: impresaconfidi@gmail.com, Certified Email: impresaconfidi@pec.it.</p>

        <h2 class="text-primary text-2xl mt-10">2. Types of data processed</h2>
        <p>Impresa Confidi processes the following personal data:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Personal and contact data (name, surname, email, telephone)</li>
          <li>Tax and administrative data</li>
          <li>Credit position and guarantee data</li>
          <li>Browsing data (IP address, pages visited) collected via technical cookies</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-primary text-2xl mt-10">3. Purpose of processing</h2>
        <p>Data is processed for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Management of the membership relationship and guarantee procedures</li>
          <li>Regulatory, accounting and tax compliance</li>
          <li>Communications regarding the Confidi's activities</li>
          <li>Response to requests sent via the contact form</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-primary text-2xl mt-10">4. Legal basis</h2>
        <p>Processing is based on the performance of the contractual/membership relationship and compliance with legal obligations.</p>

        <h2 class="text-primary text-2xl mt-10">5. Data retention</h2>
        <p>Data is retained for the time necessary to fulfill the purposes described above and in compliance with applicable regulatory obligations (10 years for tax and accounting documentation).</p>

        <h2 class="text-primary text-2xl mt-10">6. Data subject rights</h2>
        <p>Under Articles 15-22 of the GDPR, the data subject has the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access, rectification and erasure of data</li>
          <li>Restriction and objection to processing</li>
          <li>Data portability</li>
          <li>Lodge a complaint with the Data Protection Authority</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise these rights, send a request to: <strong>impresaconfidi@gmail.com</strong>.</p>

        <h2 class="text-primary text-2xl mt-10">7. Changes</h2>
        <p>This notice may be subject to changes. Please check this page periodically.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
